lead_paragraph: Poland have proved at Euro 2016 that they can compete with the best, but must now step up a level to be able to progress further in future tournaments, coach Adam Nawalka said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Poland Coach Sees Solid Base for Future Success
headline.main: Poland Coach Sees Solid Base for Future Success
